2. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper also discusses feedback control systems and the tradeoff between regulated output variance and disturbance rejection measure, which are key concepts in systems and control. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the Kalman filter algorithm, which is commonly used in machine learning for state estimation. 
4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses feedback communication systems, which are relevant to networking and internet architecture. 
5. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) - The paper discusses feedback control systems, which are relevant to multiagent systems.
